    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - IC BUS SERVICE MANUAL - DOORS AND ACCESSORIES - DOOR
        SPEED
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="adjust" graphiccount="3">
        <title>DOOR SPEED</title>
        <para>The door speed can be adjusted at the air control valve. The air valve is located above the entrance door.
            Refer to illustrations below (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700147">Figure 45</hotlnk>,
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700148">Figure 46</hotlnk>, and
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700149">Figure 47</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700147" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg47/G4700147.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 45. Opening Speed Adjustment</caption>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f4700148" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg47/G4700148.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 46. Closing Speed Adjustment</caption>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f4700149" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg47/G4700149.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 47. Jam Nut Torque</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>To change the opening speed or closing speed use the steps below:</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Use a small tip slotted screwdriver</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Loosen jam nut (hex head nut).</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the "open" screw and turn clockwise to slow speed down.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To increase the door opening speed, turn slotted screw counter-clockwise.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten jam nut.</para>
        </step1>
        <para>To change the close speed, use the steps below:</para>
        <seqlist style="arabic">
            <item>
                <para>Use a small tip slotted screwdriver.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Loosen jam nut (hex head nut).</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Locate the "close" screw and turn clockwise to slow.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>To increase the door opening speed, turn slotted screw counter-clockwise.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Tighten jam nut.</para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
    </svcproc>
